<div class="main">
  <div class="doc">
    <h1 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:8px">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <div class="updated">Last updated: January 1, 2026</div>
    <h2>1. Introduction</h2><p>Welcome to FincalMax ("we," "our," or "us"). We operate fincalmax.com. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information.</p>
    <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2><p>Calculator inputs are processed locally in your browser and never transmitted to our servers. We collect anonymous usage data via Google Analytics (pages visited, time spent, device type).</p>
    <h2>3. Google AdSense & Advertising</h2><p>We use Google AdSense to display advertisements. Google uses cookies to serve relevant ads based on your browsing history. You can opt out at <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank">Google Ads Settings</a>.</p>
    <h2>4. Cookies</h2><ul><li><strong>Essential cookies:</strong> Required for site functionality</li><li><strong>Analytics cookies:</strong> Anonymous usage data via Google Analytics</li><li><strong>Advertising cookies:</strong> Google AdSense for relevant advertisements</li></ul>
    <h2>5. Your Calculator Data</h2><p>All calculations happen entirely within your web browser. We do not collect, store, transmit, or share any financial figures you enter. Your data never leaves your device.</p>
    <h2>6. Children's Privacy</h2><p>Our site is not directed to children under 13. We do not knowingly collect information from children under 13.</p>
    <h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2><p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.</p>
    <h2>8. Contact Us</h2><p>📧 <a href="mailto:privacy@fincalmax.com">privacy@fincalmax.com</a></p>
  </div>
